OL,5, Female recruits at an army training    
OL,6, centre look less smart than their male 
OL,7, colleagues due to ill-fitting uniforms,
OL,8, an Ofsted report has found.            
OL,10,FInspectors found issues with uniforms  
OL,11,Fat Army Training Centre (ATC) Pirbright
OL,12,Fin Surrey prevented women "looking as  
OL,13,Fpresentable" as their male peers.      
OL,15,FThe report which looked at 12 training 
OL,16,Fbases also discovered "serious and     
OL,17,Fpersistent" flaws in accommodation.    
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) has been 
OL,20,Fcontacted for comment.                 
